OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry morning with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells. Bright spells
OL,7,Fcontinuing in east through the
OL,8,Fafternoon but showers increasingly
OL,9,Fdeveloping from the west. Windy at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will stay cloudier in the
OL,13,Fwest with scattered showers feeding
OL,14,Fin. Generally drier with some bright
OL,15,Fthen clear spells in the east. Windy
OL,16,Fat times.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FIt will stay mainly dry in
OL,19,Fthe east with some bright spells at
OL,20,Ftimes. Mostly cloudy in the west with
OL,21,Fsome showers. Windy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
