OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry and
OL,6,Fincreasingly sunny on Sunday. Dry and
OL,7,Fbright start on Monday, perhaps
OL,8,Fcloudier towards the coast, rain from
OL,9,Fsouthwest later. Mostly cloudy Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith rain or showers. Becoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
